pan></em></figcaption></figure></div><p></p><p>Coding agents are engineered=
 for software work where the notable parts are not only the model choice bu=
t the surrounding system, including repo context, tool design, prompt-cache=
 stability, memory, and long-session continuity.</p><p>That distinction mat=
ters because when we talk about the coding capabilities of LLMs, people oft=
en collapse the model, the reasoning behavior, and the agent product into o=
ne thing. But before getting into the coding agent specifics, let me briefl=
y provide a bit more context on the difference between the broader concepts=
, the LLMs, reasoning models, and agents.</p><h2 class=3D"header-anchor-pos=
t"><strong>On The Relationship Between LLMs, Reasoning Models, and Agents</=
strong><div class=3D"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-posit=
ion-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent"><div class=3D"pencraft pc-displ=
