n></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=3D"image-caption"><em>Figure 3. A=
 coding harness combines three layers: the model family, an agent loop, and=
 runtime supports. The model provides the =E2=80=9Cengine=E2=80=9D, the age=
nt loop drives iterative problem solving, and the runtime supports provide =
the plumbing. Within the loop, =E2=80=9Cobserve=E2=80=9D collects informati=
on from the environment, =E2=80=9Cinspect=E2=80=9D analyzes that informatio=
n, =E2=80=9Cchoose=E2=80=9D selects the next step, and =E2=80=9Cact=E2=80=
=9D executes it.</em></figcaption></figure></div><p>The takeaway here is th=
at a good coding harness can make a reasoning and a non-reasoning model fee=
l much stronger than it does in a plain chat box, because it helps with con=
text management and more.</p><h2 class=3D"header-anchor-post"><strong>The C=
oding Harness</strong><div class=3D"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-=
