f the most important ones.</p><p>When a user says =E2=80=9Cfix the tests=E2=
=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cimplement xyz,=E2=80=9D the model should know whether it=
 is inside a Git repo, what branch it is on, which project documents might =
contain instructions, and so on.</p><p>That=E2=80=99s because those details=
 often change or affect what the correct action is. For example, =E2=80=9CF=
ix the tests=E2=80=9D is not a self-contained instruction. If the agent see=
