l outputs, logs, etc.</p><p>If the runtime keeps all of that at full fideli=
ty, it will run out of available context tokens pretty quickly. So, a good =
coding harness is usually pretty sophisticated about handling context bloat=
 beyond just cutting our summarizing information like regular chat UIs.</p>=
